61. Recall the steps to delete an element from an array?
      1. Use unset($array[index]) to remove an element.
      2 .Optionally, use array_values($array) to reindex numeric arrays.
<?php
$fruits = array("Apple", "Banana", "Mango", "Orange");
unset($fruits[1]); // remove Banana
$fruits = array_values($fruits); // reindex
print_r($fruits);
?>
Output:
Array ( [0] => Apple [1] => Mango [2] => Orange )
